Steps to configure maven plugin:
- in src/main/resources create file named "manifest.standalone"
- in releng project open jSparrow.product and run Eclipse Product export wizard
- from folder created by product export go to repository/plugins/ and copy all plugins to src/main/resources
- copy all plugin names in manifest.standalone
- run mvn install on jsparrow-maven-plugin project

To run on project:
- in pom of maven project add following lines in plugins:
			<plugin>
				<groupId>at.splendit</groupId>
				<artifactId>jsparrow-maven-plugin</artifactId>
				<version>2.2.1-SNAPSHOT</version>
			</plugin>
- run mvn jsparrow:refactor